nodebasis

Class ImplicitEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • nodebasis.ImplicitEvent

  • public class ImplicitEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    The ImplicitEvent is figuratively speaking the shadow of an event which previously has occurred within the node network. It holds the id of the event and a node which knows the direction to the node where the event originated.
    Since:
    2016-05-19
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Alexander Beliaev
